<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 550px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      .header img {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .body {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .body img {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .body h2,
      .body h3 {
        color: #222;
      }

      .body p {
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        font-size: 16px;
        background-color: #0088ff;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #0077dd;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #555;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .link {
        color: #0073e6;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .link:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 479px) {
        .body {
          padding: 1rem 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/duozomapm/image/upload/v1737799706/AnuvBanner2_lp8bqd.jpg"
          alt="ANOX"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="body">
        <h2>WHERE STYLE MEETS COMFORT!</h2>
        <p class="desc">
          We’re thrilled to have you on board! Your account has been
          successfully created, and you’re all set to explore the best of ANOX
          Fashion.
        </p>
        <a href="<%= CLIENT_URL %>/" class="button">Get Started</a>

        <h3>Buy 1 Hoodie, Get 1 Free – Limited Time Offer!</h3>
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/duozomapm/image/upload/v1739466717/AdTemplate_wcmb2c.jpg"
          alt=""
        />
        <p>
          Yes, you heard it right! For a limited time, when you buy one hoodie,
          you get another one absolutely FREE. Stay warm, stylish, and double
          your fashion game with ANOX. Don’t miss out—grab yours now!
        </p>

        <h3>Oversized Fashion – The Ultimate Comfort & Style</h3>
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/duozomapm/image/upload/v1739466717/AdTemplate_wcmb2c.jpg"
          alt=""
        />
        <p>
          Love comfort and style? Our oversized collection is designed to give
          you the perfect blend of coziness and trend. Whether you're into
          oversized hoodies, tees, or both, ANOX has got you covered. Check out
          our latest arrivals today!
        </p>

        <h3>
          Your Ultimate Destination for Hoodies, Oversized Fits & T-Shirts
        </h3>
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/duozomapm/image/upload/v1739466717/AdTemplate_wcmb2c.jpg"
          alt=""
        />
        <p>
          At ANOX, we believe fashion should be effortless and expressive. Our
          collection features high-quality hoodies, oversized outfits, and
          stylish tees, perfect for every occasion. Explore our website and find
          the style that suits you best!
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Anox Clothing Brand!</p>
        <p>Best Regards,</p>
        <p>Team ANOX</p>
        <p>
          Need help?
          <a href="<%= CLIENT_URL %>/contact-us" class="link"
            >Contact us here.</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2025-2026 All rights reserved | Designed and Developed by
        <a href="https://hruthik.onrender.com">Hruthik M</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
